      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example has been maintained with a recent rod bearing service and a proactive rear subframe reinforcement\u2014essential for the chassis's structural integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. A true enthusiast's spec ready for the apex.",
