    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my car. Honestly, this has been such a fantastic ride and it\u2019s still running like a dream! It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, making it the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It\u2019s in really solid shape and ready for its next adventure with a new owner. I'm sad to see it go, but I know you're going to love driving it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
