      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a speed-sensitive M Variable Differential Lock. This example has been mechanically maintained with a focus on longevity, including a cooling system refresh and documented VANOS bulletproofing. The suspension retains its factory-tuned composure, utilizing MacPherson struts and a multi-link rear setup for precise lateral transients. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains robust and the throttle response is razor-sharp. A mechanically sound, driver-oriented example of the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-cars.",
